This page collects slides and relevant links for students in Prof. Jeff's **Tuesday section (Section 03)** of **DSAN 5100: Probabilistic Modeling and Statistical Computing**, Fall 2024 at Georgetown University.

Sections take place in **Car Barn 309** on **Tuesdays** from **6:30pm to 9:00pm**.
